data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home with modern features. Step inside to discover a spacious open-concept design that seamlessly connects the living room and dining area, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for family gatherings and entertaining friends. The main living areas boast easy-to-maintain vinyl flooring, providing a sleek and clean look while also being practical for everyday living. Say goodbye to carpet cleaning hassles! The kitchen offers ample counter space and cabinetry for all your culinary needs. You'll appreciate the convenience of a 2-car garage, providing both parking and storage space. Outside, the backyard is fenced providing a secure space for outdoor activities and enjoying the fresh air. Whether it's playing with pets or gardening, you'll have plenty of space to make it your own. This home combines modern living with practicality, making it an ideal place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new residence. Tour Today
